Package com.quantcomponents.chart.series

Interface Summary
IOHLCRenderer Interface for OHLC data points renderers
ISimpleRenderer Interface for renderers of a simple value on a chart
ITimeSeriesChartModel<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> Model for rendering of time series on a chart
ITimeSeriesChartModelListener<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> Listener to a ITimeSeriesChartModel, to be notified for each update in the data series
ITimeSeriesRenderer Interface for chart renderers of time series Implementors of this interface generally do not listen for changes in the series.

CandlestickRenderer Candlestick renderer for OHLC data points

DoubleScale Mark scale for double axis
DoubleScaleSelector Selects the correct mark scale for double axis
LevelSeriesRenderer This renderer paints a horizontal line for each level in the series, that continues until the next value in the series
OHLCSeriesRenderer Time series renderer that uses OHLC data point renderers (like candlestick renderers)
TimeAxis Chart axis for time values
TimeChartMetrics Implementation of IChartMetrics for double series indexed by Date
TimeMark Chart ruler mark for Date values
TimeRulerX Horizontal chart ruler for double charts indexed by Date
TimeScale A mark scale for chart axis with Date values This class is not thread-safe.
TimeSeriesChart SWT component displaying a time series chart
TimeSeriesChartModel<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> Implementation of ITimeSeriesChartModel for double charts indexed by Date
